The following sermons are not formally included in this bibliography as separate entries, but are present in the Brock Collection, Box 46. Only the first date is given even if the sermon was preached more than once: 

1. Cor. 15. [19.] 3/17/1822; 
Sermon on 2nd Timothy. 4. 7. 3/3/1822; 
2d. Sermon on John 1 5. 8. 1/6/1822; 
1. Timothy. 4. 8. 6/1/1817; 
Sermon on 1st Cor. 1. 20, 21 3/19/1820; 
Sermon on John 5, 41 2/20/1820; 
Sermon on John 8, 36 7/4/1809; 
Sermon on John 8, 36 7/4/1807; 
A Sermon occasion by...[Richmond fire] c12/29/1811; 
Sermon on Genesis v. 24 11/1/1818. 

Of the manuscript sermon fragments present in the collection, nine are substantial in length, but all are missing their title pages. Numerous individual and small sets of pages are also present.
